Common Question: How do I receive my certificate once I complete the program?
1.Ensure you have verified your Coursera account using the same email you were onboarded with through the WCS2 Women in Cybersecurity Scholarship Program.
2.Complete all nine courses in the Google Cybersecurity Career Certificate Program. For the full list of courses, visit our Scholarship Page or check your program details on Coursera after registration.
3.Upon successful completion, you will automatically receive your final certificate directly from Coursera by email.
